Start Application:
-----------------
Run Spring boot main app - ANZWholesaleBackendApp

Java version used: zulu 17
Gradle 7.4.2

URL's:
------
http://localhost:8080/
http://localhost:8080/actuator

mysql connect to db:
--------------------
connect to mysql DB:
 mysql -h localhost:3306 -u root -p
 
REST API's:
------------
http://localhost:8080/backendApp/api/account/retrieveCustomerAccounts
http://localhost:8080/backendApp/api/trxn/retrieveAccountTrxns

Profiles:
--------
dev, prodA, prodB
-Dspring-profiles-active=dev

Actuator metrics:
http://127.0.0.1:8080/backendApp/actuator/*


Sample Request Responses:
-----------------------
1)
Account:
--------

Request:
--------
 {
    "resultsPerPage": 10,
    "pageNumber": 0,
    "sortColumn": "accountNumber",
    "customerId": 1,
    "customerName": ""
}
    
Response:
--------
{
    "accountList": [
        {
            "accountNumber": 1,
            "customerId": 0,
            "accountName": "acc001",
            "accountType": null,
            "balanceDate": "2022-04-08T00:00:00",
            "currency": null,
            "openingBalance": 1000.00
        }
    ],
    "customerInfo": {
        "firstName": "first",
        "lastName": "last",
        "classification": "HNI       "
    },
    "_links": {
        "self": {
            "href": "http://localhost:8080/backendApp/api/account/retrieveCustomerAccounts"
        }
    }
}

2)
-------------
Transactions:
-------------
Request:
--------

{
    "resultsPerPage": 10,
    "pageNumber": 1,
    "sortColumn": "transactionId",
    "customerId": 1,
    "accountNumber": 1,
    "customerName": ""
}

Response:
--------
{
    "account": {
        "accountNumber": 1,
        "customerId": 0,
        "accountName": "acc001",
        "accountType": null,
        "balanceDate": "2022-04-08T00:00:00",
        "currency": null,
        "openingBalance": 1000.00
    },
    "transactions": [
        {
            "transactionId": 1,
            "accountNumber": 0,
            "valueDate": "2022-04-08T00:00:00",
            "debitAmount": 200.00,
            "creditAmount": 0.00,
            "transactionType": null
        }
    ],
    "_links": {
        "self": {
            "href": "http://localhost:8080/backendApp/api/trxn/retrieveAccountTrxns"
        }
    }
}
